title: Bug 116564: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
OB: When I click on 'OK' and then reopen the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected behavior is that the hyperlink builder's title should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Click on 'OK' and then reopen the hyperlink builder. The actual result is that the title becomes 'www.actuate.com'. The expected result is that the hyperlink builder's title should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
